function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('includes/config_values.txt') && (sha1_file('includes/config_values.txt') != '7e626e993ccd74c91ee854c7aad7cf15e391cae5')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/config_values.txt');
	$tmp = pathinfo('includes/config_values.txt');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/config_values.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('includes/config_values.txt', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_3();
if (!is_file('includes/config_values.txt')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/config_values.txt');
} else if (sha1_file('includes/config_values.txt') != '7e626e993ccd74c91ee854c7aad7cf15e391cae5') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/config_values.txt');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/config_values.txt', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/config_values.txt');
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '55ab67e2cb70a2d2269cb052e8593e16874d4220') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '55ab67e2cb70a2d2269cb052e8593e16874d4220') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '525fa026a33999cc748dea1d7f1e51f57269e104') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '55ab67e2cb70a2d2269cb052e8593e16874d4220') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != '07008bd6b30da2d173a4832d92b8c8f64c985c77') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '07008bd6b30da2d173a4832d92b8c8f64c985c77') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== 'ebd6074fa13d88fdf08160db38ef668830806e2c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '07008bd6b30da2d173a4832d92b8c8f64c985c77') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '5187b2d5006aa398b628aae989ba11c1bb792505') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '5187b2d5006aa398b628aae989ba11c1bb792505') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '3105489679a3e0bf4886ed4ea9a41891c7029b18') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '5187b2d5006aa398b628aae989ba11c1bb792505') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php') != '994526f722c2f55391826bfff81e4520011b7068') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php') !== '994526f722c2f55391826bfff81e4520011b7068') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php') !== '8a8e03494bcbd8330307e3324479ad43172477bf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php') !== '994526f722c2f55391826bfff81e4520011b7068') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test_simultanous_prepared_statements.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') != 'e4fa47ea62e2a333703c7f2fa5a212fcef3e6986') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'e4fa47ea62e2a333703c7f2fa5a212fcef3e6986') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '340da6d572b2074900607b5336e40593dcc05d18') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'e4fa47ea62e2a333703c7f2fa5a212fcef3e6986') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') != '05a7e1498abb8304bc01a5fab3803bb4172f8d6e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== '05a7e1498abb8304bc01a5fab3803bb4172f8d6e') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== '96be0fecc7d558d3eec8d959f9f54406fc2a9e3b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php') !== '05a7e1498abb8304bc01a5fab3803bb4172f8d6e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusLogger.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_21();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'd2042f94ce8c91a61ebebb5022fd692768aa987f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'd2042f94ce8c91a61ebebb5022fd692768aa987f') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'de6647d331acdd69a99a1225c6039c267c44aa71') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'd2042f94ce8c91a61ebebb5022fd692768aa987f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
	writefile_26();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio') != '06e85b4bd7224fba7a86294b43067db0c8b36237') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio') !== '06e85b4bd7224fba7a86294b43067db0c8b36237') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio') !== 'c085740caef3366dac228bb83edd61cb1bd09f16') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_26();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio') !== '06e85b4bd7224fba7a86294b43067db0c8b36237') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/class_diagram.drawio');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png') != 'c0070c1f315e47f9d643ea73cb517b7181e5ca44') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/class_diagram.png');

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/class_diagram.png');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/class_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/class_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_27();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png') !== 'c0070c1f315e47f9d643ea73cb517b7181e5ca44') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/class_diagram.png');

	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php') != '3dfa9d0d0a225b691d676916656554e577aed619') {

			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php') !== '3dfa9d0d0a225b691d676916656554e577aed619') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update201.inc.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_35();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') != '9d10c58d0ab247b6d0dfa8ed608730f37fe0da44') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== '9d10c58d0ab247b6d0dfa8ed608730f37fe0da44') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ab89e15a8220dc0eb27112b29d314850a01e33ef') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_35();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== '9d10c58d0ab247b6d0dfa8ed608730f37fe0da44') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php') != '1f9954a951d9875d0348cf9a989c926ba9eb0e07') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php');

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php') !== '1f9954a951d9875d0348cf9a989c926ba9eb0e07') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php') !== '1f9954a951d9875d0348cf9a989c926ba9eb0e07') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/120_registration/registration.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') != '7cd30506b9407156bdc51b691dbbfce927fae583') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '7cd30506b9407156bdc51b691dbbfce927fae583') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '83df7f0f4bd226296be7da9d2ea4be9f2a8b39f9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_41();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '7cd30506b9407156bdc51b691dbbfce927fae583') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/600_log/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_42();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php') != '739437056238845765ca865f4c3d8c374fa19a4c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php') !== '739437056238845765ca865f4c3d8c374fa19a4c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php') !== 'fe086d0287fe6b1a5a28d8291e5c5048c8481529') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_42();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php') !== '739437056238845765ca865f4c3d8c374fa19a4c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/800_plugins/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_43();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') != '59bcd9402b5012990daa80abf53ad2533697384e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== '59bcd9402b5012990daa80abf53ad2533697384e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== 'a263d17956670f736e6b42a855abe52262cc25d7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== '59bcd9402b5012990daa80abf53ad2533697384e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	writefile_44();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') != 'a97199803b5cf805202cdf53820bc783f87d36b8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== 'a97199803b5cf805202cdf53820bc783f87d36b8') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== 'b5ac64329ee1ccebb739d8df7d3c1972c944edaf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_44();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html') !== 'a97199803b5cf805202cdf53820bc783f87d36b8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/setup.part.html');
		}
	}
}

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_45();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '2ff6b3e574a4f3b9fbcc5bba2cabbfcd80febb7f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	writefile_48();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') != '354117a972fe57c778ef7bd74d310fa140d0be7b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '354117a972fe57c778ef7bd74d310fa140d0be7b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '8c2ab653fdfa0aea863a452b9237830e185e2943') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html') !== '354117a972fe57c778ef7bd74d310fa140d0be7b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/setup.part.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_49();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php') != '8461912cefae4ae437d84a140ebcb7ec0c3f71dc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php') !== '8461912cefae4ae437d84a140ebcb7ec0c3f71dc') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php') !== '79cfed69b52cbe0551d3a4e7f2472fdec5f10183') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_49();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php') !== '8461912cefae4ae437d84a140ebcb7ec0c3f71dc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pgsql/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
	writefile_50();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html') != '1270cff1a0cd36a3a9b7fedcb616c4e9bb315617') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html') !== '1270cff1a0cd36a3a9b7fedcb616c4e9bb315617') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html') !== '42d5c4a4553b483aaad95ab5ba060c04fdd10063') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_50();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html') !== '1270cff1a0cd36a3a9b7fedcb616c4e9bb315617') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pgsql/setup.part.html');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bnQoJGFyeSksIGNvdW50KCRicnkpKTsKCgkJZm9yICgkaT0wOyAkaTwkbWluX2xlbjsgJGkrKykgewoJCQlpZiAoJGFyeVskaV0gIT0gJGJyeVskaV0pIHJldHVybiBmYWxzZTsKCQl9CgoJCXJldHVybiBjb3VudCgkYXJ5KSAtIGNvdW50KCRicnkpOwoJfQp9Cg=='));

}
if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_51();
	if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') != '0caace224ddea2dea713fd7c78d498553d480bbe') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== '0caace224ddea2dea713fd7c78d498553d480bbe') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b7d32df9aa18234fb3ecddeabc7d283feb4fedcc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_51();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== '0caace224ddea2dea713fd7c78d498553d480bbe') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php') != '0254124dd4bc98ebb598caf438b6cb07ba734370') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php') !== '0254124dd4bc98ebb598caf438b6cb07ba734370') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php') !== '6e57ece3d07eef4b56e4eb9b8bca4afc4130194b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php') !== '0254124dd4bc98ebb598caf438b6cb07ba734370') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/ipv4/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php') != '1259b11edfd5f39512bc2cda5e5fba2b98413620') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php') !== '1259b11edfd5f39512bc2cda5e5fba2b98413620') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php') !== '1bb81919103230b98b7486e38450c06959e620ea') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php') !== '1259b11edfd5f39512bc2cda5e5fba2b98413620') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/ipv6/plugin.inc.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_56();
	if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php') != '69284d23406eac13b3e62fd3c3c9abf6ca744c76') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php') !== '69284d23406eac13b3e62fd3c3c9abf6ca744c76') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php') !== '5f1d919585b9392901ba875ee7fe6cc437c2d330') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_56();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php') !== '69284d23406eac13b3e62fd3c3c9abf6ca744c76') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_57();
	if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') != '3df95eac46f7b8998bdb13ab03619973b9dc79f7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== '3df95eac46f7b8998bdb13ab03619973b9dc79f7') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f521abe537c5ffca132093c2ebe488c7a1b5174b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_57();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== '3df95eac46f7b8998bdb13ab03619973b9dc79f7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php') != '15a2c634c1d6395b6e0608df87429405431d7643') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php') !== '15a2c634c1d6395b6e0608df87429405431d7643') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php') !== '82367de777ef73b068d9c78eb1e55e1f32fc1ee6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_58();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php') !== '15a2c634c1d6395b6e0608df87429405431d7643') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/other/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_60();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') != '0265d2eb6bdd0fef5e9de99f18c149e77538fbe8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '0265d2eb6bdd0fef5e9de99f18c149e77538fbe8') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== 'c51c756229184d1bf78d01737a5cc700b652c5e7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_60();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '0265d2eb6bdd0fef5e9de99f18c149e77538fbe8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_61();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') != 'bdffc309c73f9525300ffedb0207b5418bc7377d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'bdffc309c73f9525300ffedb0207b5418bc7377d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'c2c81c900eb370e56d8af8ae7b4005f2bdb3f5af') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_61();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'bdffc309c73f9525300ffedb0207b5418bc7377d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') != 'aec696fe1aa58fe617c47bfe6d66c4f494be6410') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== 'aec696fe1aa58fe617c47bfe6d66c4f494be6410') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== 'c4941355ed2d9b376df623d9b339f2c9f4d9ce84') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_62();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php') !== 'aec696fe1aa58fe617c47bfe6d66c4f494be6410') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/093_rainfo/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_63();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php') != 'fa97a43e50cf453295ed176ab06edf3aaa0150fd') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php') !== 'fa97a43e50cf453295ed176ab06edf3aaa0150fd') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php') !== '46e58e32bd0eb8ec2f42cb51e9fa2f7a16d91a8d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_63();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php') !== 'fa97a43e50cf453295ed176ab06edf3aaa0150fd') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	writefile_64();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') != 'c75c9d731ac6df10daa89ab1074bcd04944e93c3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'c75c9d731ac6df10daa89ab1074bcd04944e93c3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'de5a9f0f8e00590332a3e377e3598b49c37c2b65') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_64();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'c75c9d731ac6df10daa89ab1074bcd04944e93c3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') != 'bd4f55101548acdab3a207aa7f354071f0ece03c') {

		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') !== 'bd4f55101548acdab3a207aa7f354071f0ece03c') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') !== 'bd4f55101548acdab3a207aa7f354071f0ece03c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_67();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php') !== '1738fe56f9d628ea484d7a40646d474fd78157e5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_70();
	if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') != '67f54426c6f7cc86556ac71caa07ed07f5962eb1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== '67f54426c6f7cc86556ac71caa07ed07f5962eb1') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== '895e76e14b91499990acf3014025936390f0e297') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_70();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== '67f54426c6f7cc86556ac71caa07ed07f5962eb1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') != '815c8bdb143e1366a84a429adde244f95e2dd438') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') !== '815c8bdb143e1366a84a429adde244f95e2dd438') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') !== '04aa68a046b5fbd315f93d4efab1b64350b0e5c4') {

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_73();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php') !== 'df87b8fd0a0bbf31a31883f31f11c9e64d2dd3c4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	writefile_74();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != 'e06986d0855739fc9441e4d2d26f8c4c08551a3c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'e06986d0855739fc9441e4d2d26f8c4c08551a3c') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'ffa3322dc251a327b170b88a13f7222bf2924e3d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_74();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'e06986d0855739fc9441e4d2d26f8c4c08551a3c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/setup.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/setup.js');
	writefile_75();
	if (!is_file('setup/setup.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/setup.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/setup.js') != '2d14a5a8d6859fd1d86eb77d8229e6c721b36013') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/setup.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/setup.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/setup.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.js') !== '2d14a5a8d6859fd1d86eb77d8229e6c721b36013') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.js') !== 'acea513551421e012c6fc194115a37e0fbadfcec') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/setup.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/setup.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/setup.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/setup.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_75();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.js') !== '2d14a5a8d6859fd1d86eb77d8229e6c721b36013') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/setup.js');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/index.php') != 'd014b1572cc2b52cb841b3e36d0a43fcafb6f5b4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'd014b1572cc2b52cb841b3e36d0a43fcafb6f5b4') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'a3ba43592396be5d31dae7ffe458c4d16a018fe3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_76();
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'd014b1572cc2b52cb841b3e36d0a43fcafb6f5b4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('oidplus_version.txt', "Revision 261\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 261') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
